NO un

00:13:53.839 --> 00:13:55.388
v-

00:13:55.388 --> 00:13:56.820
vu hot ir gevoynt?

00:13:56.722 --> 00:13:57.542
KFAR-SABA.

00:13:58.142 --> 00:14:01.680
ir hot gezogt az ayer man hot men glaykh genumen in militer.

