hot, ansht-, anshtot tsu gebn SUG ALE- UNK SUG ALEF hot men im gegebn

00:14:19.731 --> 00:14:20.996
GIML DALED.

00:14:20.704 --> 00:14:22.318
 vos meynt dos?

00:14:20.996 --> 00:14:22.317
er zol UNK

00:14:22.763 --> 00:14:27.873
, az- azoy vi s'iz do arbet (ober) se zaynen di b-, di beste, s'iz do ergere un nokh ergere.

00:14:27.873 --> 00:14:29.456
un im hot men gegebn di ergstn.

00:14:30.610 --> 00:14:33.135
dernokh hob i- dernokh hob ikh farshvangert, un

00:14:33.141 --> 00:14:34.620
im genumen in militer.

00:14:34.525 --> 00:14:36.493
m'hot im genumen in militer.

