00:15:32.068 --> 00:15:34.306
s'ken zayn, vayl ikh hob (far)shvangert zeyer kleyn.

00:15:34.377 --> 00:15:35.184
yo.

00:15:36.118 --> 00:15:38.697
ir zaynt geblibn in Erets-Yisroel tsen yor.

00:15:38.597 --> 00:15:39.327
elf.

