00:16:01.887 --> 00:16:02.978
m- tate.

00:16:03.051 --> 00:16:04.226
hot im nit gekent.

00:16:04.283 --> 00:16:07.604
un ikh hob gezen az mir hobn nit key- s'iz nit, nit laykht far undz.

00:16:07.604 --> 00:16:10.664
