ir v- ir zaynt ongekumen in nayntsn akht un fuftsik.

00:16:54.070 --> 00:16:54.580
ye.

00:16:54.246 --> 00:16:55.847
vos hot ir do geton?

00:16:55.954 --> 00:17:00.285
do fun onfang hob ikh gearbet als a, in, in, in

00:17:01.050 --> 00:17:03.356
in a dos o, vi heyst es? oy.

00:17:04.948 --> 00:17:06.140
in a yeshive.

00:17:06.805 --> 00:17:08.250
in Kamenitser yeshive.

00:17:09.166 --> 00:17:10.780
vos i- bin ikh geven a kekhin.

00:17:11.547 --> 00:17:13.718
un di kinder?

00:17:13.925 --> 00:17:15.859
zaynen gegangen

00:17:13.992 --> 00:17:17.240
di kinder zaynen glay-, zay zaynen UNK gegangen in SCHOOL.

