00:17:24.287 --> 00:17:28.111
fun onfang zaynen zey gegangen in a PU- PUBLIC SCHOOL, vayl ikh bin gegangen aynkoyfn bay eyne.

00:17:28.658 --> 00:17:31.211
hot zi, hot zi zikh mit undz tseredt, (ot) zogt zi "far vo-"

00:17:31.211 --> 00:17:36.803
un zi hot mir nor geholfn zey zoln aynordenen in PUBLIC SCHOOL. dernokh iz gekumen a bakante, zogt zi "far vos geyen zey p- in PUBLIC SCHOOL?"

00:17:37.129 --> 00:17:41.021
un zi hot shoy- zogt ir mayn man, "ikh ken nit tsoln di yeshive", zogt (er) "kum, ikh vel zey aynordenen."

00:17:41.382 --> 00:17:43.823
zaynen zey gegangen a shtikl tsayt in di yeshive.

00:17:44.588 --> 00:17:45.898
biz di bal-mitsve.

